TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT D_EMPLOYEE.EMP_KEY as EMP_KEY, D_EMPLOYEE.EMP_NAME as EMP_NAME, D_EMPLOYEE.ADDRESS as ADDRESS, D_EMPLOYEE.CITY as CITY, D_EMPLOYEE.STATE as STATE, D_EMPLOYEE.COUNTRY as COUNTRY, D_EMPLOYEE.CURRENT_FLAG as CURRENT_FLAG, D_EMPLOYEE.CURRENT_VERSION as CURRENT_VERSION, D_EMPLOYEE.START_DT as START_DT, D_EMPLOYEE.END_DT as END_DT, D_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID as EMP_ID FROM D_EMPLOYEE WHERE END_DT LIKE TO_DATE('9999-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD')
